<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Booking Rejected</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    "
  >
    <table
      style="
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      "
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center">
          <h1 style="color: #dc3545">Booking Rejected</h1>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
          <p>
            We regret to inform you that your booking has been rejected. The
            details are as follows:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <p><strong>Booking Type:</strong> <%= bookingType %></p>
            <p><strong>Pickup Location:</strong> <%= pickupLocation %></p>
            <p><strong>Pickup Date:</strong> <%= pickupDate %></p>
            <p><strong>Reason for Rejection:</strong> <%= rejectionReason %></p>
          </ul>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or would like to discuss further, please
            don't hesitate to contact us.
          </p>
          <p>Best regards,<br />Ethio Smart Ride Transportation</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
